Adding Project Title and Project Logo 12

Steps 1

Adding Project Title 

·         Click on the Text box from Home Menu

·         Begin typing the name of the project (Conflicts in Ethiopia (1997 - 2015)

·         Turn the background to “off” position.

·         Select the text then change the font size to 28 and font type to Segoe (Bold) and choose center for Alignment

·         select the text then font color to #000000 and Alignment center.

·         General:  X - Position = 21, Y - Position = 19, Width = 1251 and Height = 69

 


Steps 2

Adding Project Logo

1.    Click on Insert from the Menu.

2.    Then click on Image

3.    Select the Image from the file

4.    General:  X - Position = 1171, Y - Position = 20, Width = 109 and Height = 70
